WHAT THIS REPOSITORY IS
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

This repository contains the overnight batch processing pipeline for Archnemix ShortGen — an automated system for generating Reddit-style YouTube Shorts from text scripts using AI-driven text-to-speech, forced alignment, subtitle generation, and video encoding.

This repository is made PUBLIC solely to take advantage of GitHub's unlimited Actions minutes for public repositories. The public visibility of this repository does NOT constitute an open-source release, a public domain dedication, or a grant of any rights whatsoever to any party.

